Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.90,0:01:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mana será renascida consumindo Inori.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.33,0:01:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nossa Eva perdida...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.42,0:01:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,É tarde demais,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.92,0:01:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shu.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.67,0:01:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso não pode ser!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.69,0:02:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.07,0:02:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Que luz é essa?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.44,0:02:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Algo está começando a acontecer!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.99,0:02:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Não há dúvida disso.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.95,0:02:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo. Vamos contê-los aqui.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.62,0:02:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Suba o mais rápido possível.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.20,0:02:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayase! Cubra-os!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.91,0:02:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado! Mas...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.37,0:02:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Você realmente me pegou da última vez.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.75,0:02:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas desta vez será diferente!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.17,0:02:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Agora, eu tenho o Gespenst!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.47,0:02:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi, você ainda não consegue retomar o controle?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.73,0:02:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,As defesas ficaram subitamente mais fortes!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.56,0:02:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu continuo tentando apagar isso, mas ele volta como um zumbi!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.90,0:02:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Alguém no nível de Tsugumi...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.86,0:02:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenji...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.86,0:02:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,É você?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.93,0:03:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Bom dia, Triton.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.97,0:03:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Vejo que você acordou, Mana.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.02,0:03:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Shu!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.52,0:03:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou muito feliz!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.36,0:03:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Você veio por mim!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.78,0:03:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Foi terrível!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.07,0:03:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Havia uma mulher incômoda que não parava de me atrapalhar!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.49,0:03:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas agora está tudo certo.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.41,0:03:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu a esmaguei e tomei este corpo como meu!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.25,0:03:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,O que ela estava pensando?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.63,0:03:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Aquele monstro feito pelo homem.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.05,0:03:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Pare!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.63,0:03:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shu!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.84,0:03:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A Inori não é um monstro!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.84,0:04:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ela chorou por mim!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.89,0:04:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Você parece e soa igual, mas ela não é como você!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.06,0:04:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ela é humana!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.19,0:04:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Você é cruel, Shu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.15,0:04:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sua irmã mais velha te ama tanto.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.95,0:04:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu amei você mesmo quando meu corpo foi reduzido a trapos.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.41,0:04:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas ainda assim,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.24,0:04:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Você me rejeita de novo, Shu!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.87,0:04:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Pare aí mesmo.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.67,0:04:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Gai?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.09,0:04:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Deixe o resto comigo.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.32,0:05:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Você me machucou, Shu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.70,0:05:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Se você machucar alguém, deve estar preparado para receber a mesma quantidade em troca.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.33,0:05:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu não vou te perdoar
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.25,0:05:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,mesmo que você peça desculpas.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.36,0:05:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso é...!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.07,0:05:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Começou, Gai.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.01,0:06:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Há valores de ressonância genômica mais altos que Lost Christmas vindo de Tóquio!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.51,0:06:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Está afetando até o sistema de controle remoto do Endlave!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.43,0:06:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Isto é...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.18,0:06:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,O Quarto Apocalipse começou.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.60,0:06:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A evolução e seleção da vida neste planeta.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.52,0:06:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.32,0:07:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Descartem nossos corpos fracos e alcancem uma consciência eterna dentro dos cristais.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.87,0:07:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Essa é a próxima fase.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.87,0:07:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Os Voids foram apenas um sinal de um novo mundo,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.37,0:07:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,onde os corações são matéria!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.46,0:07:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,É porque você está usando armamento comum!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.22,0:07:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nós vamos esmagar você!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.68,0:07:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Não vamos deixar você!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.10,0:07:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Não nos subestime, seu filho da puta!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.44,0:07:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayase! Conecte com um cabo!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.66,0:07:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi! Um programa de evasão!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.74,0:07:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.79,0:07:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sua vadia!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.54,0:08:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.30,0:08:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.67,0:08:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenente Daryl!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.76,0:08:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,O Emulador de Genoma Void ainda está sendo testado!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Não exagere no uso!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.26,0:08:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do que você está falando?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.06,0:08:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu não vou parar até ter massacrado todos eles!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.40,0:08:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Souta!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.86,0:08:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Gai!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.24,0:08:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Em Roppongi, você disse que salvaria a Mana!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.45,0:08:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Você me mandou te apunhalar para salvá-la!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.20,0:08:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Como chegamos a isso?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.41,0:08:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Você não consegue entender, Shu.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.26,0:08:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Você foi escolhido, mas escolheu soltar!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.14,0:08:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Você nunca vai entender!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.52,0:09:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,E aí, Kurosu?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.32,0:09:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A garota que você tentou salvar está acabando com o mundo.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.24,0:09:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu venci.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.20,0:09:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Você fez isso com o mundo...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.78,0:09:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Para Shu... só por isso?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.95,0:09:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Não vou negar.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.46,0:09:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Você vai me atirar,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.88,0:09:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.42,0:09:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Não posso deixá-los passar.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.72,0:09:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu os distrairei.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.68,0:09:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Por ele...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.77,0:09:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Que persistência!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.61,0:09:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Droga, eu não consigo acompanhar!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.23,0:09:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.98,0:09:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Aguente até o meu sinal.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.45,0:09:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Você consegue fazer isso?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.24,0:09:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Quem você pensa que está falando?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.79,0:10:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Naquela época, eu teria deixado você
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.96,0:10:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,ter Mana e o lugar de Adão.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.88,0:10:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas agora, você não é digno.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.59,0:10:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Morra, Shu.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.43,0:10:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Meu corpo está entorpecido.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.18,0:10:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu vou morrer aqui?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.81,0:10:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Com o Void de todos em mim?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.92,0:10:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Não desista, Shu.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.71,0:10:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Você ainda pode se mover.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.59,0:10:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo mundo está esperando por você.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.44,0:11:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Por favor, todo mundo...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.19,0:11:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Use-me!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.71,0:11:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.59,0:11:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.22,0:11:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenji,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.43,0:11:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,É xeque-mate.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.86,0:11:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Existem pessoas
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.40,0:11:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,que confiaram suas vidas em mim.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.70,0:12:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu não posso morrer aqui.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.83,0:12:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenho certeza de que vou recuperar a Inori.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.72,0:12:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Agora!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.80,0:12:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayase, desculpa por esperar!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.26,0:12:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.77,0:12:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Deixa o controle remoto comigo!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.65,0:12:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Gai...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.90,0:12:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Não se meta no meu caminho.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.77,0:12:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu vou te derrotar com tudo que eu tenho!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.95,0:12:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Essa voz...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.32,0:12:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu sabia. Você está aqui, não é?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.41,0:12:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.20,0:12:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.58,0:12:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.71,0:12:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Se eu te tirar de cena, posso ser eu mesmo!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.13,0:12:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu posso ser o açougueiro Daryl!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.38,0:13:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Cala a boca! Nós vamos fritar você primeiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.15,0:13:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Inori?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.08,0:13:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.21,0:13:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nós conseguimos?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.60,0:13:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Irmão!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.90,0:13:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No final, o vencedor não foi nem Kurosu, nem eu.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.94,0:14:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Vai, Haruka.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.37,0:14:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Gai!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.66,0:14:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Está tudo bem, Shu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.58,0:14:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Apenas seja você mesma.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.35,0:14:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Onde eu estou?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.94,0:14:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,O lugar onde a seleção converge.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.07,0:14:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,O mundo além do Apocalipse.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.40,0:14:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Gai...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.90,0:14:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Isto é
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.49,0:14:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,a utopia de Da'at.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.41,0:14:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo este planeta se transformará em
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.45,0:14:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,memórias dentro dos cristais.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.42,0:15:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Fui celebrado como um rei,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.75,0:15:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,mas no final...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.34,0:15:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu sempre tive medo de ser deixado para trás.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.10,0:15:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Esse é o motivo pelo qual
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.35,0:15:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu queria a Eve...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.98,0:15:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mana.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.44,0:15:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Lá atrás,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.19,0:15:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,quando você nos esfaqueou em Roppongi,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.44,0:15:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,eu acreditei que a Mana seria libertada dessa forma.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.78,0:15:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas Da'at,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.91,0:15:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,a vontade da seleção natural
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.29,0:15:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,não permitirá que Mana morra.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.08,0:15:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mesmo que ela morresse, ela seria reanimada de novo.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.34,0:15:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Há apenas uma maneira de salvá-la.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.55,0:15:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,É deixá-la terminar o papel dela.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.35,0:15:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Foi por isso que eu arrisquei.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.48,0:15:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu me tornaria o próprio diabo e traria o Apocalipse.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.15,0:16:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Então você viria para nos parar.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.49,0:16:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Meu papel termina aqui.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.20,0:16:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Gai!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.82,0:16:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Agora vá
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.87,0:16:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,e salve Inori.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.34,0:16:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Shu...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.89,0:16:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shu...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.64,0:16:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Não se culpe...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.35,0:16:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.52,0:16:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenho muitos sentimentos por você.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.15,0:16:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,É tudo.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.28,0:16:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Graças a você.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.70,0:16:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ei, Shu...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.62,0:17:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Onde você está?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.29,0:17:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Shu?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.76,0:17:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shu...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.47,0:17:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Por favor, fique comigo.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.10,0:17:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu estou do seu lado.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.56,0:17:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.60,0:17:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Inori...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.65,0:17:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos juntos.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.81,0:17:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Esse sentimento!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.18,0:18:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu senti também!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.18,0:18:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,É o Ouma!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.61,0:18:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shu! Você vai se tornar o novo Salvador?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.24,0:18:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Toda a estrutura está em caos por causa do Cristal Genoma!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.71,0:18:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo o prédio vai desmoronar em breve!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.50,0:18:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Pessoal...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.34,0:18:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Doutor Ouma! Você não está machucado?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.47,0:18:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Você?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.51,0:18:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Se você tiver outra chance,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.89,0:18:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,seja mais gentil com as pessoas!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.22,0:18:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No fundo, você era um cara legal, Daryl!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.49,0:18:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu consigo sentir os corações de todos fluindo em minha direção.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.78,0:18:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,As memórias deles...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.33,0:19:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mesmo as pessoas que me odiavam nasceram
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.45,0:19:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,e foram amadas por alguém.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.67,0:19:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Inori...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.59,0:19:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Leva.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.15,0:19:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Inori!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.92,0:19:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Espera! O Shu ainda está lá dentro!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.80,0:19:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu sei!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.01,0:19:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas eu não posso deixar você morrer aqui também!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.06,0:20:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shu!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.78,0:21:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ei, Yahiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.54,0:21:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Você está cedo.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.71,0:21:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Está ocupado com trabalho?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.79,0:21:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mais ou menos.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.33,0:21:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas eu saí cedo hoje.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.96,0:21:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Posso sentar aqui?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.22,0:21:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Claro.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.67,0:21:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayase, você se importa com um Earl Grey?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.39,0:21:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso é muito gentil da sua parte, Tsugumi.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.89,0:21:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Só por hoje.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.85,0:21:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Os exames de professor estão chegando, então eu vou virar demônio de novo em casa.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.94,0:21:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele ainda não chegou?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.27,0:21:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele estará aqui.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.48,0:21:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele estava ansioso por isso.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.28,0:21:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, lá está ele!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.74,0:21:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Faz um tempo, não é?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.37,0:21:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Desculpe a espera.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.33,0:21:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Então, ao ano deste ano!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.34,0:21:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Saúde!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.05,0:21:27.06,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(200,200)}Hoje você não me ama mais
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.68,0:21:33.69,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(200,200)}nem eu sou mais valorizado por você
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.06,0:21:42.49,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(200,200)}Agora estou completamente sozinho
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.28,0:21:50.37,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(200,200)}O que você me disse quando nos separamos?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.00,0:21:57.00,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(200,200)}As palavras pairaram no ar e nunca chegaram até mim
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.46,0:22:03.76,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(200,200)}Eu sei que meus sonhos e desejos são ilusórios
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.34,0:22:10.39,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(200,200)}e ainda assim não consigo desistir deles
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.48,0:22:20.44,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(200,200)}Você disse: "Não solte, segure minha mão
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.99,0:22:27.45,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(200,200)}e: "Estaremos sempre juntos
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.62,0:22:36.21,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(200,200)}Suas mãos, quando eu as segurei, estavam quentes
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.34,0:22:44.51,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(200,2000)}e suaves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.15,0:00:15.33,OP_S2,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\blur4.5\fad(100,75)\t(\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&)}A realidade da destruição ao nosso redor preenche nossa mente
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.25,0:00:26.38,OP_S2,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\blur4.5\fad(100,300)\t(\3c&H000000&\c&HFFFFFF&)}A chuva torrencial soa como uma tempestade de lágrimas
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.76,0:00:29.34,OP_S2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\3c&H000000&}Perceba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:30.01,OP_S2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&}que seus olhos foram dados a você para se aceitarem,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.01,0:00:31.30,OP_S2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&}que seus olhos foram dados a você para se aceitarem,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:32.22,OP_S2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&}que seus olhos foram dados a você para se aceitarem,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.22,0:00:34.10,OP_S2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&}que seus olhos foram dados a você para se aceitarem,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:34.76,OP_S2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&}que seus olhos foram dados a você para se aceitarem,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.76,0:00:40.10,OP_S2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(100,150)\t(\3c&H000000&)}que sua voz foi dada a você para dizer aos outros como você se sente
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.40,0:00:49.99,OP_S2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(100,150)}{\3c&H000000&}e que suas mãos foram dadas para segurar quem você ama
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:54.20,OP_S2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(100,150)\3c&H000000&}Todas as coisas vivas
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:57.79,OP_S2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(100,150)\3c&H000000&}Todos os seres vivos que podem ouvir esta canção,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:01:02.38,OP_S2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(100,150)\3c&H000000&}Sua verdade está dentro do seu coração
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:05.25,OP_S2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(100,150)\3c&H000000&}Mesmo ao cruzar um mar tempestuoso,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.59,0:01:11.84,OP_S2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(100,150)\3c&H000000&}Ela te dará força que nunca vacilará
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.18,0:01:17.64,OP_S2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(100,150)\3c&H000000&}e{\3c&H000000&}um destino,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.27,0:01:21.44,OP_S2,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(100,350)\3c&H000000&}Realmente
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.15,0:00:15.33,OP_S2_roma,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\blur4.5\fad(100,75)\t(\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&)}Uma sinfonia de colapso ecoa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.25,0:00:26.38,OP_S2_roma,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\blur4.5\fad(100,300)\t(\3c&H000000&\c&HFFFFFF&)}A chuva antiga tem a cor das lágrimas
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.76,0:00:29.34,OP_S2_roma,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\3c&H000000&}Kizuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:34.76,OP_S2_roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&\c&HFFFFFF&}Seus olhos são para reconhecer um ao outro,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.76,0:00:40.10,OP_S2_roma,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(100,150)\t(\3c&H000000&)}Sua voz é para transmitir sentimentos
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.40,0:00:49.99,OP_S2_roma,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(100,150)}{\3c&H000000&}Sono te wa daiji na hito to tsunagu tame ni aru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:54.20,OP_S2_roma,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(100,150)\3c&H000000&}Kono uta ga kikoeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:57.79,OP_S2_roma,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(100,150)\3c&H000000&}Inochi aru subete no mono yo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:01:02.38,OP_S2_roma,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(100,150)\3c&H000000&}Shinjitsu wa anata no mune no naka ni aru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:05.25,OP_S2_roma,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(100,150)\3c&H000000&}Mesmo ao atravessar o mar de tempestades
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.59,0:01:11.84,OP_S2_roma,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(100,150)\3c&H000000&}A força que jamais será esquecida
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.18,0:01:17.64,OP_S2_roma,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(100,150)\3c&H000000&}K{\3c&H000000&}u{\3c&H000000&}r{\3c&H000000&}e{\3c&H000000&}r{\3c&H000000&}u{\3c&H000000&} k{\3c&H000000&}a{\3c&H000000&}r{\3c&H000000&}a
